Programme  大会程序表
===================
8.00am 
Arrival of Venerable Monks, Invited Guests & Devotees
欢迎僧伽，贵宾及佛友出席

8.30am
Dhamma talk by Venerable Monk 
师父开示

9.15am 
Paying homage to the Triple Gem, observing three refuges and five precepts
礼敬三宝及受三皈依五戒

9.30am 
Speech by organising Chairman of Sanghikadana
筹委会主席致词

9.45am 
Dhamma talk by Venerable Monk
师父开示

10.30am 
Offering of robes and requisites to the venerable Sangha
供奉袈裟及必需品 予僧伽

10.45am 
Paritta chanting by Venerable Monks and sharing of merits
僧众诵祝福经及回向功德

11.00am 
Pindapatta by monks and lunch (self service) for devotees
师父托钵及佛友用餐

For Further  information，Kindly contact  
更多详情，敬请联络
